<paragraph base="F55666545" principles="yes" id="IFRS17_78"><paranum>78</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 17"/><data name="paranum" value="78"/></prolog><body><bodydiv base="IFRS2020-3">     <p id="IFRS17_P0302">An entity shall present separately in the statement of financial position the carrying amount of portfolios of: </p>     <ol base="F55666547" type="lower-alpha" id="IFRS17_L0058"><li id="IFRS17_78_a"><li_value>(a)</li_value>         <p base="F55666548" id="IFRS17_P0303"><xref base="F55666957" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0532">insurance contracts<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0186"/></ph></xref> issued that are assets;</p>       </li><li id="IFRS17_78_b"><li_value>(b)</li_value>         <p base="F55666550" id="IFRS17_P0304">insurance contracts issued that are liabilities;</p>       </li><li id="IFRS17_78_c"><li_value>(c)</li_value>         <p base="F55666552" id="IFRS17_P0305"><xref base="F55667022" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0554">reinsurance contracts<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0323"/></ph></xref> held that are assets; and</p>       </li><li id="IFRS17_78_d"><li_value>(d)</li_value>         <p base="F55666554" id="IFRS17_P0306">reinsurance contracts held that are liabilities.</p>       </li></ol></bodydiv></body></paragraph>